      <xref href="../tasks/t_validate-single-file.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="xref:1;40:57">Validate a single file</xref>
      to reproduce the failure locally, then
      <xref href="../tasks/t_read-validation-report.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="xref:2;42:59">read the validation report</xref>
      to fix it. You do not need to read this topic first.
    </note>

    <section id="the-problem" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="section:1;46:31">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="title:2;47:14">What it does</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="p:1;48:10">Your team defines rules once in a JSON file. The tool applies them to every
      article and reports exactly which rules each file passes or fails — catching
      missing fields, stale dates, wrong values, and structural issues that reviewers
      would otherwise flag manually.</p>

      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="p:2;53:10">markdown-validator checks two parts of each file:</p>
      <table id="what-it-checks-table" class="- topic/table " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="table:1;54:40">
        <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="tgroup:1;55:26">
          <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.5*" class="- topic/colspec " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="colspec:1;56:52" colnum="1"/>
          <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3*" class="- topic/colspec " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="colspec:2;57:54" colnum="2"/>
          <thead class="- topic/thead " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="thead:1;58:18">
