          </thead>
          <tbody class="- topic/tbody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="tbody:1;61:18">
            <row class="- topic/row " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="row:2;62:18">
              <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="entry:3;63:22" colname="col1" dita-ot:x="1" dita-ot:y="2"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="b:3;63:25">Front-matter metadata</b> — the YAML <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;63:70">---</codeph> block</entry>
              <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="entry:4;64:22" colname="col2" dita-ot:x="2" dita-ot:y="2">Required fields present, values match allowed values, date is
              recent, naming conventions</entry>
            </row>
            <row class="- topic/row " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="row:3;67:18">
              <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="entry:5;68:22" colname="col1" dita-ot:x="1" dita-ot:y="3"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="b:4;68:25">Document body</b> — content below the front matter</entry>
              <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_what-is-markdown-validator.dita" xtrc="entry:6;69:22" colname="col2" dita-ot:x="2" dita-ot:y="3">Exactly one H1, required H2 sections present, heading
